Customer Reviews

Great shop! Decent prices for the products they are selling. Definitely worth the drive out. They even have low waste natural vegan sunscreen that doubles as bug spray. I've never seen a cool product like that. Make sure you bring some containers to fill up if you want to buy some things. If you forget, though, they have jars and other containers that they can provide! -Henry

The laundry detergent is the best. I can vouch for the fact that one tablespoon does a full load! Also the silk lotion is the best I’ve ever used! - Ingrid

Friendly service, clean store. Very glad to have such a broad selection available in a local refill store! Got the DW detergent pods, some liquid dish soap, and facial astringent. Looking forward to trying more products as we use up what we've bought already! -Cameron

Love this store! Excellent customer service and products. -Kayla
